lead_paragraph: At a stunned Etihad Stadium, Leicester City fans crooned "and now you're gonna believe us we're gonna win the league", while across England a delighted footballing community began to sense they may just be right.

headline.print_headline: Leicester-The Football Fairytale That Keeps on Giving
